      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7 and boil a full kettle</p><p>Top, tail and slice your <strong>courgette[s]</strong> into discs</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1712067885140-x200.jpg",
