        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> cooled wilted kale & spinach </strong>to a <strong>food processor </strong>with your<strong> basil</strong>,<strong> grated Italian hard cheese </strong>and <strong>half</strong> the<strong> chopped garlic </strong>(you'll use the rest later!)</p><p>Add<strong> </strong>2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span><strong> olive oil</strong> with 4 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[6 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[8 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold water </strong>and a generous pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and<strong> pepper</strong></p><p>Blitz until very finely chopped – this is your <strong>kale & basil</strong> <strong>pesto</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1712067897490-x200.jpg",
